Package: polybar
Architecture: any
Depends: ${misc:Depends}, ${shlibs:Depends}
Description: fast and easy-to-use status bar
 Polybar aims to help users build beautiful and highly customizable status 
 bars for their desktop environment, without the need of having a black belt
 in shell scripting.
